## 🧑🏾‍🏫 what this challenge teaches u
Endianness tells which order to store bytes
u can store them in 2 ways:
- Big Endian -> in the 'normal' order, from MSB to LSB. it is used in Networking
- Little Endian -> the order is opposite: from LSB to MSB. it is used in processors to allow efficiency
so in this case since the python line in cimg file explains "little", we need reverse the bytes

